venue.address_1: 1245 Worcester Road, free standing building by the Natick Collection
venue.name: Cheesecake Factory

item.description: A casual get together for drinks, food and fun times with other friendly people. Relax and have fun! Everyone pays for their own food/drinks.
item.how_to_find_us: We'll start at the bar area and then move to a table. Look for Catherine (see photo). I'll be wearing/carrying a red jacket and have a large red purse. Please call 774 232 0000, if you have trouble finding us!
item.why: Have fun chatting with other friendly and interesting people in their 20's and 30's who live/work in the Metro West area. Low key, no pressure, everyone pays for their own food/drinks. Just come and enjoy yourself!
item.name: Meet up for drinks, food and good times at the Cheesecake Factory, Natick
